I"Ç<p>These are the image sizes needed for universal iOS applications - including iPad, iPad Retina, iPhone 3.5‚Äù, iPhone 4‚Äù, iPhone 4‚Äù Retina, iOS &gt;=6 and iOS 7. Images should be PNGs at 24 BPP.</p>

<p>An iPhone app needs the 4‚Äù launch screens present, otherwise the app will run at 3.5‚Äù on the 4‚Äù device (letterboxed).</p>

